Subject: Webportal is currently down
Description:
hello Support,
I am unable to access the webportal to perform a user group audit.  It is showing a 503 error any idea on what can be done
Solution_Comment__c:
Issue
AIC portal is not loading properly, presenting a 503 error upon trying to access it.

Cause
The service account associated with NEA was updated with a new password but the relevant IIS settings were accidentally overlooked and not updated.

Resolution
Updating the IIS server with the new service account credentials allowed the AIC portal to start loading correctly again.
